.SH NAME
mn \- create a Mininet network.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B mn
[\fI\,options\/\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
(type mn \fB\-h\fR for details)
.PP
The mn utility creates Mininet network from the command line. It can create
parametrized topologies, invoke the Mininet CLI, and run tests.
